    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:0",
      "translation": "RfH 由谁开发？",
      "words": [
        "RfH"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:1",
      "translation": "这是由 SideFx 与 Pixar 的 RenderMan group（RenderMan 团队）共同开发的。",
      "words": [
        "SideFx",
        "Pixar",
        "RenderMan",
        "group",
        "RenderMan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:2",
      "translation": "RfH 与 RenderMan release（RenderMan 版本发布）同步的频率如何？",
      "words": [
        "RfH",
        "RenderMan",
        "release",
        "RenderMan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:3",
      "translation": "我们会尽量在 RenderMan release（RenderMan 版本）可用后尽快同步。对于大型版本，例如 major version change（主版本变更，而不是 point release 小版本发布），这需要时间，尤其是在 Houdini 尚未支持新功能 UI 时。",
      "words": [
        "RenderMan",
        "release",
        "RenderMan",
        "major",
        "version",
        "change",
        "point",
        "release",
        "Houdini",
        "UI"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:4",
      "translation": "如何报告 bug 和建议？",
      "words": [
        "bug"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:6",
      "translation": "RenderMan for Houdini 论坛",
      "words": [
        "RenderMan",
        "for",
        "Houdini"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:8",
      "translation": "当我不确定遇到的是 Houdini bug 还是 RenderMan bug 时，应该在哪里报告？",
      "words": [
        "Houdini",
        "bug",
        "RenderMan",
        "bug"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:11",
      "translation": "；然后，如果问题与 RenderMan shaders（RenderMan 着色器）和 output（输出）相关，请在",
      "words": [
        "RenderMan",
        "shaders",
        "RenderMan",
        "output"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:12",
      "translation": "RenderMan for Houdini 论坛",
      "words": [
        "RenderMan",
        "for",
        "Houdini"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "36a202dcc6:13",
      "translation": "提交 bug。",
      "words": [
        "bug"
      ]
    }
